    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Let''s introduce you a new type of zombies: the sound sensitive zombie.

        These
        zombies are former soldiers who died during the Great War.


        They
        are very sensitive with sound and will rush and attack where they hear a
        sound.

        This makes them even more dangerous but also really useful
        as they don''t only attack you, but anything that is close from the sound
        position.


        Try to break the crate on the left to make the soldier
        kill the other zombie.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
