    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Oh, also, note that, in the same way they investigate when hearing
        a sound, when they lost their sight with you, zombies will come and investigate
        on the last known place they saw you at.


        So, don''t stay on the
        same spot after escaping from a zombie.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
