    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Zombies can also hear you in addition to see you.

        If you need
        to get really close from a zombie you can CROUCH to stay undetected.


        Try
        it with the zombie in this alley.

        As soon as you don''t dollide
        with it, it''s okay.


        If anything goes wrong, I have weakened it,
        a simple punch should kill it.'
