    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Zombies have another dangerous attribute you should know about. When
        you kill them, they are not really dead.

        If you get close to a "dead"
        zombie, it could revive and restart its routine, or even attack you.


        So
        be careful because that only happens when you come close to one.


        Try
        this by going away and then getting close from this zombie.

        Don''t
        worry you can punch it too kill it instantly!'
