    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "Okay, you are ready to get in a real life testing zone!\nYou will encounter
        real and dangerous zombies in this zone. I taught you everything you had
        to know and I trust you, you will make it.\n\nPlease find me at the end of
        this zone so I can bring you back to our base, you will be safe there. \nOh,
        one last thing. If you directly shoot on a zombie it will get angry and chase
        you, so you should avoid doing this if it's not for a good reason.\n\nSee
        you on the other side, I'm waiting for you!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
