    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Be careful, you enter in a dangerous zone where there are zombies.


        You
        will be able to test how zombies can see you. They have 3 parameters :

        -
        Sight range

        - Sight angle

        - Obstruction check: if you''re
        behind an obstacle blocking the line of sight


        If they see you,
        it will be harder to get out from their sight so prefer hiding behind something
        like a wall


        The walls here turn red when it can see you, else they
        are green'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
