    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'As I said earlier, zombies can hear sounds. When hearing something
        they will go and investigate on the position of the sound.

        This
        is really useful if you want to attract them at a place.


        But don''t
        take too much time because the zombie will come back from where it comes
        after having investigated the zone!


        Try breaking the crate by shooting
        on, it will make a noise and attract the near zombie.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
