    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'If a zombie is too sticky with you you have a way to get rid of it.

        If
        you shoot several times in a row, the zombie will react to the shots and
        stop moving for some seconds, letting you the time to run away.


        Try
        shooting 3 times on the next zombie to see its reaction.'
