    - target: {fileID: 5189707445226607746, guid: 18a629e4d73825248883441efdc60d05, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'You may have seen that, but the more you watch at a zombie, the more
        your sight will decrease and a weird effect will appear.

        This is
        because you are watching something horrific like a zombie or blood.


        Your
        sanity decreases little by little. But don''t worry, you can revert the effect
        rapidly by watching at another place.

        The sound you will hear will
        also be different

        Try this with the next zombie and by shooting
        around when you are under the effect.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
